<paragraph id="940D9A4BFFF1FFA08748FA6B4C2AFA0D" blockId="74.[264,1311,1444,1510]" box="[264,1311,1444,1510]" pageId="74" pageNumber="75">
<emphasis id="A6C64659FFF1FFA08748FA6B48B0FA56" box="[264,389,1444,1469]" italics="true" pageId="74" pageNumber="75">Etymology</emphasis>
Named in reference to the emarginated posterior edge of the larval cephalic apotome.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="940D9A4BFFF1FFA08748F9D34A17F9B5" blockId="74.[264,802,1564,1630]" box="[264,802,1564,1630]" pageId="74" pageNumber="75">
